data.actual_result: No matter in which order the links are placed in the message, embeds for invite links will always display as the last one
data.expected_result: As on Desktop, the first embed should be the one for invite link, and other embeds from other links apear below the invite embed
data.short_description: Invite embeds always appear as the last embed
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to a channel with embed links permissions - Write a message containing several links, the first one being a Discord server invite - Send the message and observe the order of the embeds
